{"type":"message","id":"1a64c552","parentId":"fc5452b5","timestamp":"2026-04-03T01:54:54.928Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_md287K7vIQFMGspZjPBDzo","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Save task\ncat > /home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-9/reviews/pending_task_ideator_stage2.json << 'TASKEOF'\n{\n  \"target\": \"ideator\",\n  \"port\": 18820,\n  \"token\": \"ideator-hook-2026\",\n  \"sessionKey\": \"hook:p9-stage2-idea\",\n  \"created_at\": \"2026-04-03T09:54\",\n  \"status\": \"pending\"\n}\nTASKEOF\n\n# Send task to Ideator\nRESPONSE=$(curl -s -w \"\\n%{http_code}\" --max-time 30 \\\n  -X POST http://127.0.0.1:18820/hooks/agent \\\n  -H 'Authorization: Bearer ideator-hook-2026' \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{\n    \"message\": \"当前项目：/home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-9\\n以下 SHARED = 上述路径\\n\\n## 任务：生成研究创意\\n\\n### 研究主题\\n基于多模态大模型（Multimodal Large Language Models, MLLM）的智能故障诊断\\n\\n### 目标期刊\\nIEEE TIM\\n\\n### 调研摘要（关键gap）\\n1. 缺乏专门针对工业多模态数据（振动+图像+文本）预训练的LLM，零样本故障诊断性能差\\n2. 真实工业场景中跨模态噪声和模态缺失处理不足\\n3. 缺乏标准化的多模态LLM故障诊断benchmark\\n4. LLM在安全关键故障诊断中的可解释性不足\\n5. 边缘部署的可扩展性和实时推理能力缺乏\\n\\n### 创新方向参考\\n- 多模态LLM预训练用于零/少样本故障诊断\\n- VLM跨模态检索系统\\n- 物理信息引导的LLM因果故障推理\\n- 高效融合的混合LLM-Transformer边缘部署\\n\\n### 要求\\n1. 生成 5 个创意候选，每个包含：\\n   - 英文标题\\n   - 核心创新点（2-3句）\\n   - 技术路线概述\\n   - 预期贡献（3-4条）\\n   - 可行性评估（高/中/低）\\n   - 新颖性评估（高/中/低）\\n2. 创意必须适合 IEEE TIM 风格（偏工程应用，非纯理论）\\n3. 必须涉及多模态 + 大模型 + 故障诊断三个关键词\\n4. ⚠️ 只列出创意，不要替用户选择\\n\\n### 输出\\n写入：/home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-9/ideas/idea_candidates.md\",\n    \"name\": \"P9-Stage2-Idea\",\n    \"sessionKey\": \"hook:p9-stage2-idea\"\n  }')\nHTTP_CODE=$(echo \"$RESPONSE\" | tail -1)\necho \"HTTP: $HTTP_CODE\"","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"claude-proxy","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":62986,"output":758,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63744,"cost":{"input":0,"output":