{"type":"message","id":"2fc56aed","parentId":"108189a7","timestamp":"2026-04-03T01:57:31.363Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_78ZcsltcSDXKL51lrWKkRx","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Create outline v1 directory\nmkdir -p /home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-9/outline/v1\n\n# Save task\ncat > /home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-9/reviews/pending_task_architect_stage3.json << 'TASKEOF'\n{\n  \"target\": \"architect\",\n  \"port\": 18830,\n  \"token\": \"architect-hook-2026\",\n  \"sessionKey\": \"hook:p9-stage3-outline\",\n  \"created_at\": \"2026-04-03T09:56\",\n  \"status\": \"pending\"\n}\nTASKEOF\n\n# Send task to Architect\nRESPONSE=$(curl -s -w \"\\n%{http_code}\" --max-time 30 \\\n  -X POST http://127.0.0.1:18830/hooks/agent \\\n  -H 'Authorization: Bearer architect-hook-2026' \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{\n    \"message\": \"当前项目：/home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-9\\n以下 SHARED = 上述路径\\n\\n## 任务：设计论文框架\\n\\n### 选定主题\\nRobustMLLM-Diag: Adaptive Cross-Modal Imputation and Fusion in Multimodal Large Language Models for Noisy Fault Diagnosis\\n\\n### 核心创新\\n- MLLM中的自适应融合机制，通过跨模态检索和去噪动态补全缺失模态\\n- 不确定性感知注意力机制，对噪声工业数据流进行加权\\n- 在20-50%模态丢失或噪声条件下实现可靠诊断\\n\\n### 技术路线\\n1. 模态特定编码器 + 不确定性估计（Bayesian dropout）\\n2. RAG跨模态补全\\n3. 端到端训练（模拟噪声/缺失数据）+ RL鲁棒性优化\\n4. 在增强工业数据集上验证\\n\\n### 黄金标准（必须严格遵守）\\n- 结构：Abstract, I.Introduction, II.Theoretical Background, III.Proposed Method, IV.Experiments, V.Conclusion, References\\n- 字数：Abstract~190词, Intro~900词(≤1000), Background~1150词, Method~1650词, Experiments~2650词, Conclusion~190词, 总计~7200词\\n- 引用：35篇目标，Intro引用≥总引用50%\\n- 图：8-15张（概念图用figure*双栏）\\n- 表：6-12个\\n- 公式：8-15个\\n- Intro贡献列表3-4条\\n- 最后一段描述论文组织结构\\n\\n### 范例论文结构参考\\n读取以下文件了解IEEE TIM论文风格：\\n- /home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-9/examples/example1_parsed/example1/auto/example1.md\\n- /home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-9/examples/example2_parsed/example2/auto/example2.md\\n\\n### 输出要求\\n写入 /home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-9/outline/v1/paper_outline.md，包含：\\n1. 完整论文标题\\n2. 每个section/subsection的标题\\n3. 每个section/subsection的内容要点（bullet points）\\n4. 每个section的目标字数\\n5. 图表规划（编号、标题、类型、位置）\\n6. 公式规划（编号、内容描述）\\n7. 引用分配计划（每section预计引用数）\",\n    \"name\": \"P9-Stage3-Outline\",\n    \"sessionKey\": \"hook:p9-stage3-outline\"\n  }')\nHTTP_CODE=$(echo \"$RESPONSE\" | tail -1)\necho \"HTTP: $HTTP_CODE\"","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"claude-proxy","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":67520,"output":1032,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68552,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775181428949}}
