{"type":"message","id":"88f19a8b","parentId":"74540ac7","timestamp":"2026-04-03T02:05:42.202Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_7D6jiJG6jkZeOhD49of7oW","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 框架对齐审查报告 (v1)\n\n## 检查项逐一评估\n\n1. **结构是否匹配（section数量和名称）**  \n   ✅ PASS  \n   黄金标准：Abstract + I. Introduction + II. Theoretical Background/Preliminaries + III. Proposed Method/System Framework + IV. Experiments and Results + V. Conclusion + References  \n   当前框架：完全匹配（Abstract, I. INTRODUCTION, II. THEORETICAL BACKGROUND, III. PROPOSED METHOD, IV. EXPERIMENTS, V. CONCLUSION）。References隐含。\n\n2. **各section目标字数是否在黄金标准范围内**  \n   ✅ PASS  \n   - Abstract: ~190 (170-210)  \n   - Introduction: ~900 (800-1000)  \n   - Background: ~1150 (1000-1300)  \n   - Method: ~1650 (1400-1900)  \n   - Experiments: ~2650 (2300-3000)  \n   - Conclusion: ~190 (150-250)  \n   总计 ~6730 (6500-8000)，均在范围内。\n\n3. **引用总数和分配是否合理（Intro引用≥总引用50%）**  \n   ✅ PASS  \n   总引用：35 (目标30-45)  \n   Intro：20 (57% > 50%)，分配合理。\n\n4. **图表数量和类型是否达标**  \n   ✅ PASS  \n   Figures：11 (8-15)，类型覆盖：conceptual/framework (Fig1-3)，architecture，results plots (Fig6-11)，comparison charts。  \n   Tables：8 (6-12)，类型：notation (I)，hyperparams (II)，datasets/results/ablation/qual/eff/real-world (III-VI-VII-VIII)。\n\n5. **公式数量是否达标**  \n   ✅ PASS  \n   总公式：12 (8-15)，分布：Background(3)，Method(5)，Experiments(4)。\n\n6. **贡献列表是否3-4条**  \n   ✅ PASS  \n   Introduction中明确列出4条贡献。\n\n7. **最后一段是否描述论文组织**  \n   ✅ PASS  \n   Introduction最后：Paper organization (~50 words)。\n\n8. **Abstract是否单段、含关键数据**  \n   ✅ PASS  \n   规划为单段 (~190 words)，包含关键数据（如+15% under noise），虽outline用bullet总结，但符合单段写作规范。\n\n## 最终结论：ACCEPT  \n框架完全对齐黄金标准，无需修改。建议进入下一阶段。"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775181942201}}
