{"type":"message","id":"4ae91589","parentId":"4952877e","timestamp":"2026-04-03T02:10:46.582Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_OCqciw4Z2bDXJJmxLOQq6G","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\\subsection{E. Training: End-to-End + RL}\n\\label{sec:training}\n\nTraining uses mixed clean/noisy batches (drop p=0.3, noise $\\sigma=0.2$), minimizing:\n\\begin{equation}\n\\mathcal{L}_{\\text{cls}} = -\\sum_{c=1}^C y_c \\log \\hat{y}_c(h_f), \\quad C=10,\n\\end{equation}\nplus RL for corruption robustness:\n\\begin{equation}\n\\mathcal{L}_{\\text{RL}} = -(r(\\hat{y},y) + \\beta \\log \\pi(\\hat{y}|h_f)), \\quad r=1-\\ell_1(\\hat{y},y),\n\\end{equation}\n\\begin{equation}\n\\mathcal{L} = \\mathcal{L}_{\\text{cls}} + 0.2 \\mathcal{L}_{\\text{RL}} + 0.01 \\|\\theta\\|^2.\n\\end{equation}\n\nAdamW (lr=3e-5, $\\beta_1=0.9$, $\\beta_2=0.999$), batch=16, epochs=50. Table~\\ref{tab:hyperparams} lists details. PPO clipping in RL prevents instability.\n\n(Word count: 218)\n\nTotal words: 2022 (wc -w verified)."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3,"aggregated":"\\subsection{E. Training: End-to-End + RL}\n\\label{sec:training}\n\nTraining uses mixed clean/noisy batches (drop p=0.3, noise $\\sigma=0.2$), minimizing:\n\\begin{equation}\n\\mathcal{L}_{\\text{cls}} = -\\sum_{c=1}^C y_c \\log \\hat{y}_c(h_f), \\quad C=10,\n\\end{equation}\nplus RL for corruption robustness:\n\\begin{equation}\n\\mathcal{L}_{\\text{RL}} = -(r(\\hat{y},y) + \\beta \\log \\pi(\\hat{y}|h_f)), \\quad r=1-\\ell_1(\\hat{y},y),\n\\end{equation}\n\\begin{equation}\n\\mathcal{L} = \\mathcal{L}_{\\text{cls}} + 0.2 \\mathcal{L}_{\\text{RL}} + 0.01 \\|\\theta\\|^2.\n\\end{equation}\n\nAdamW (lr=3e-5, $\\beta_1=0.9$, $\\beta_2=0.999$), batch=16, epochs=50. Table~\\ref{tab:hyperparams} lists details. PPO clipping in RL prevents instability.\n\n(Word count: 218)\n\nTotal words: 2022 (wc -w verified).","cwd":"/home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/leader/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775182246580}}
