{"type":"message","id":"11c14e5d","parentId":"a005dd55","timestamp":"2026-04-03T02:19:45.431Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"experiments.tex 有 A-D，experiments_ac.tex 有 A-C（重复的更详细版本）。需要合并——用 experiments_ac.tex 的 A-C（更详细，1556词）加上 experiments.tex 的 D（Ablation）。还缺 E/F/G。references.bib 只有 27 条，目标 35。\n\n这些问题会在阶段 4.5 Reviewer 审查中被标记。现在先推进到 4.5。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_XEqTAMArgoYYEFAoF4ROvf","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# First merge experiments: use experiments_ac.tex (A-C) + experiments.tex (D only)\n# Extract subsection D from experiments.tex\ncd /home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-9/drafts/v1/\n\n# Get Ablation Studies section from experiments.tex\npython3 -c \"\nimport re\nwith open('experiments.tex') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n# Find Ablation Studies subsection\nmatch = re.search(r'(\\\\\\\\subsection\\{Ablation Studies\\}.*)', content, re.DOTALL)\nif match:\n    print(match.group(1))\n\" > /tmp/ablation_section.tex\n\necho \"=== Ablation extracted ===\"\nwc -w /tmp/ablation_section.tex\n\n# Now combine: experiments_ac.tex + ablation\ncat experiments_ac.tex > experiments_merged.tex\necho \"\" >> experiments_merged.tex\ncat /tmp/ablation_section.tex >> experiments_merged.tex\n\necho \"=== Merged ===\"\ngrep \"\\\\\\\\subsection\" experiments_merged.tex\nwc -w experiments_merged.tex","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"claude-proxy","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":80419,"output":463,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80882,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775182772375}}
