{"type":"message","id":"0ec00d86","parentId":"caf4bbd9","timestamp":"2026-04-03T05:22:33.084Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_69137d199cd74ca5bf3a5f83","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== v3 vs v5 comparison ===\n  abstract: v3=178w vs v5=168w\n  introduction: v3=812w vs v5=812w\n  background: v3=1030w vs v5=1030w\n  method: v3=1635w vs v5=1588w\n  experiments: v3=2514w vs v5=2459w\n  conclusion: v3=202w vs v5=172w\n=== Golden std targets ===\n  abstract: 190 (170-210)\n  intro: 900 (800-1000)\n  background: 1150 (1000-1300)\n  method: 1650 (1400-1900)\n  experiments: 2650 (2300-3000)\n  conclusion: 190 (150-250)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":11,"aggregated":"=== v3 vs v5 comparison ===\n  abstract: v3=178w vs v5=168w\n  introduction: v3=812w vs v5=812w\n  background: v3=1030w vs v5=1030w\n  method: v3=1635w vs v5=1588w\n  experiments: v3=2514w vs v5=2459w\n  conclusion: v3=202w vs v5=172w\n=== Golden std targets ===\n  abstract: 190 (170-210)\n  intro: 900 (800-1000)\n  background: 1150 (1000-1300)\n  method: 1650 (1400-1900)\n  experiments: 2650 (2300-3000)\n  conclusion: 190 (150-250)","cwd":"/home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/leader/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775193753080}}
{"type":"message","id":"902d4a93","parentId":"0ec00d86","timestamp":"2026-04-03T05:22:41.432Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"v3 is the best version across all sections. Let me use v3 as the final draft and proceed to integration. The API issues from 11:03 onwards caused the parallel session's de-AI (4.7) to truncate things, but v3 was preserved.\n\nNow I should:\n1. Confirm v3 as the final draft version\n2. Proceed to integrate into paper.tex (stage 5 - Editor/Leader integration)\n3. Then stages 6-8 (Checker, Reviewer final, PDF compile)\n\nLet me do this efficiently as Leader.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Project 9 进度汇报：\n\n从 11:03 起 API 短暂故障（502/503），Writer 和 Reviewer 多个任务失败。但之前的工作已保全。\n\n**当前状态：阶段 4.6 已完成，准备阶段 5（Editor 整合）**\n\nDrafts v3（最佳版本）：\n| Section | 词数 | 目标 | 状态 |\n|---------|------|------|------|\n| Abstract | 178 | 190 | ✅ |\n| Introduction | 812 | 900 | ✅ |\n| Background | 1030 | 1150 | ✅ |\n| Method | 1635 | 1650 | ✅ |\n| Experiments | 2514 | 2650 | ✅ |\n| Conclusion | 202 | 190 | ✅ |\n| 总计 | ~6371 | 7200 | 88% |\n| references.bib | 57 条 | 35 | ✅ |\n\nv3 是当前最佳版本（v4/v5 被去 AI 痕迹过程中截短，已恢复）。现在进入阶段 5：Editor 整合所有 section 到 paper.tex。要我继续推进吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro","usage":{"input":740,"output":536,"cacheRead":108608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109884,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775193753084}}
