{"type":"message","id":"e71cff66","parentId":"de5fbbbf","timestamp":"2026-04-03T05:39:08.297Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Experiments: 2493→2489w (slight decrease of 4 words, acceptable within 5% margin)\nConclusion: 202→206w (slight increase, good)\n\nBoth are within acceptable range. Now I need to do 4.7 de-AI. Since Writer tends to truncate, I'll do it myself as Leader - scan for AI patterns and make targeted replacements in each file.\n\nLet me do 4.7 myself as Leader - scan for common AI patterns and replace them.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Both done ✅:\n- Experiments: 2493→2489w (within tolerance)\n- Conclusion: 202→206w ✅\n\n**4.6 润色完成。** 进入 4.7 去 AI 痕迹。这次我（Leader）自己做，避免 Writer 截短。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b2064ed5ec3349b5b1094916","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"SHARED=\"/home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-9/drafts/v3\"\n\n# Scan for common AI phrases across all tex files\necho \"=== AI phrase scan ===\"\nfor pattern in \"In this paper\" \"In this article\" \"This paper proposes\" \"We propose\" \"novel approach\" \"novel method\" \"state-of-the-art\" \"it is worth noting\" \"it should be noted\" \"Furthermore\" \"Moreover\" \"Additionally\" \"In order to\" \"due to the fact that\" \"in terms of\" \"plays a crucial role\" \"have attracted increasing attention\"; do\n  count=$(grep -l \"$pattern\" \"$SHARED\"/*.tex 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\n  [ \"$count\" -gt 0 ] && echo \"  '$pattern': found in $count file(s)\"\ndone","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro","usage":{"input":214,"output":523,"cacheRead":117568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118305,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775194739306}}
