{"type":"message","id":"3be43e47","parentId":"6e183de3","timestamp":"2026-04-03T05:50:47.337Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Checker is online. Let me dispatch the LaTeX review task.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_25c3799b14864edc853a7c28","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"RESPONSE=$(curl -s -w \"\\n%{http_code}\" --max-time 30 \\\n  -X POST http://127.0.0.1:18880/hooks/agent \\\n  -H 'Authorization: Bearer checker-hook-2026' \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{\n    \"message\": \"当前项目：/home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-9\\n以下 SHARED = 上述路径\\n\\n## 任务：LaTeX 审查修复（阶段 6）\\n\\n### 审查文件\\n读取：/home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-9/final/v1/ 下所有 .tex 文件\\n\\n### 审查要点\\n1. LaTeX 语法错误检查（括号匹配、特殊字符转义、环境闭合）\\n2. 表格格式检查（\\\\begin{table}...\\\\end{table} 闭合、列数一致、\\\\hline 完整）\\n3. 公式环境检查（\\\\begin{equation}...\\\\end{equation} 闭合、\\\\label 与 \\\\ref 匹配）\\n4. 引用检查（所有 \\\\cite{key} 在 references.bib 中有对应条目）\\n5. cross-reference 检查（\\\\ref{sec:*}, \\\\ref{eq:*}, \\\\ref{tab:*} 与 \\\\label 匹配）\\n6. 排版检查（段落间距、空行规范、特殊字符如 ~, \\\\textasciitilde 等）\\n7. IEEE TIM 格式检查（abstract 单段、keywords、section 编号）\\n\\n### 输出要求\\n1. 如果发现需要修复的问题，直接修改文件\\n2. 将审查报告写入：/home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-9/reviews/latex_check_v1.md\\n3. 报告格式：每项检查 ✅ PASS 或 ❌ FIXED + 修改说明\",\n    \"name\": \"P9-Stage6-Checker\",\n    \"sessionKey\": \"hook:p9-stage6-checker\"\n  }')\nHTTP_CODE=$(echo \"$RESPONSE\" | tail -1)\necho \"HTTP: $HTTP_CODE\"","timeout":60}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro","usage":{"input":150,"output":572,"cacheRead":140160,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":140882,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775195436583}}
