{"type":"message","id":"d0b14f3d","parentId":"e9cd805b","timestamp":"2026-04-03T05:56:04.590Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_39c71e8d902d4df980a2a6b1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# LaTeX Check Report v1\\n\\n## Project: paper-project-9\\n## Reviewed: final/v1/\\n## Date: 2026-04-03\\n\\n### 1. LaTeX Syntax Errors ✅ PASS\\nNo fatal syntax errors. All braces/environments closed properly.\\n\\n### 2. Table Formats ✅ PASS\\nTables (e.g., tab:notation, tab:results) properly closed, columns consistent, hlines complete.\\n\\n### 3. Equation Environments ✅ FIXED\\nDuplicate \\\\label{eq:wasserstein} in background.tex and method.tex: renamed method to eq:wasserstein2.\\nDuplicate \\\\label{subsec:rag}: renamed method to subsec:rag2.\\nAll eq envs closed; labels/refs match post-fix.\\n\\n### 4. Citation Completeness ❌ FIXED\\nMany undefined cites initially (e.g., wen2017). Fixed: bibstyle plain→IEEEtran; ieee1888 @standard→@misc. All keys now resolve (warnings reduced).\\n\\n### 5. Cross-References ✅ PASS\\n\\\\ref{sec:background} etc. resolve. Fig refs undefined due to missing figs/ dir (reported below).\\n\\n### 6. Typography ✅ PASS\\nProper ~ for unbreakable spaces; no raw &/% etc. Minor underfull hboxes (cosmetic).\\n\\n### 7. IEEE TIM Format ✅ PASS\\nAbstract: single para. Keywords present. Sections numbered. lettersize option removed.\\n\\n## Additional Issues\\n- Missing figs/ dir: figs/fig6_snr.pdf etc. → draft mode. Create figs/ with images or comment \\\\includegraphics.\\n- BibTeX warnings minimized; some empty fields (lu2024 journal).\\n\\n## Final Status\\n✅ Compilation succeeds (paper.pdf generated, 11 pages).\\nFixed: 4 issues. Remaining: figures (content, not format).\\n\\n**Ready for Editor review.**"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775195764586}}
{"type":"message","id":"e13fddf9","parentId":"d0b14f3d","timestamp":"2026-04-03T05:56:15.722Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Checker passed. Fixed 2 issues: duplicate labels and bib style. Now dispatch Reviewer for stage 7 (final alignment review).","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Checker ✅，修复了 2 个问题（重复 label、bib style）。继续派 Reviewer 阶段 7 最终对齐审查："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9781b92489094925be9dd279","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"RESPONSE=$(curl -s -w \"\\n%{http_code}\" --max-time 30 \\\n  -X POST http://127.0.0.1:18850/hooks/agent \\\n  -H 'Authorization: Bearer reviewer-hook-2026' \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{\n    \"message\": \"当前项目：/home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-9\\n以下 SHARED = 上述路径\\n\\n## 任务：最终对齐审查（阶段 7）\\n\\n### 审查对象\\n读取：/home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-9/final/v1/paper.tex 及所有 section .tex 文件\\n\\n### 黄金标准\\n读取：/home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-9/golden_standard.json\\n\\n### 审查要点\\n1. 全文词数是否在 6500-8000 范围内\\n2. Abstract 是否单段、170-210 词\\n3. Introduction 是否 800-1000 词，引用 ≥ 总引用 50%\\n4. Background 是否 1000-1300 词\\n5. Method 是否 1400-1900 词\\n6. Experiments 是否 2300-3000 词\\n7. Conclusion 是否 150-250 词\\n8. 引用总数 30-45 篇\\n9. 所有 \\\\cite{} 与 references.bib 匹配\\n10. 公式数量 8-15\\n11. 图表规划完整（虽然图片未生成，检查引用完整性）\\n12. IEEE TIM 格式合规\\n\\n### 输出\\n写入：/home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-9/reviews/final_review_v1.md\\n结论：ACCEPT 或 REVISE\",\n    \"name\": \"P9-Stage7-Review\",\n    \"sessionKey\": \"hook:p9-stage7-review\"\n  }')\nHTTP_CODE=$(echo \"$RESPONSE\" | tail -1)\necho \"HTTP: $HTTP_CODE\"","timeout":60}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro","usage":{"input":532,"output":635,"cacheRead":141120,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":142287,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":177519576459