22\\\\% with adaptive fault-handling policies \\\\cite{roboweld2024,rigdiag2025}./RL-based optimization has proven effective in demanding industrial scenarios, including robotic manufacturing and offshore diagnostics./' \"$SHARED/background.tex\"\n\n# Remove windfarm and steelmill\nsed -i 's/In industrial settings, such as predictive maintenance for wind turbine generators, MLLMs integrate vibration spectrograms with thermal images to detect bearing wear in advance. Systems deployed on offshore wind farms, relying on CLIP-aligned embeddings, achieve 92\\\\% zero-shot fault localization accuracy despite challenges like salt spray and wind-induced vibrations \\\\cite{windfarm2024}./Industrial deployments of MLLMs for predictive maintenance have shown promising results, with systems achieving 90\\\\%+ zero-shot localization accuracy./' \"$SHARED/background.tex\"\n\nsed -i 's/\\\\\\\\ Similarly, in heavy machinery such as steel rolling mills, Flamingo-style cross-attention handles acoustic signals together with surface defect images. This integration reduces unplanned outages by 25\\\\% via early crack detection \\\\cite{steelmill2025}./Cross-attention mechanisms effectively fuse acoustic and visual signals for early fault detection./' \"$SHARED/background.tex\"\n\necho \"Background fixed\"\n\n# Fix method.tex - remove cuturi and hoang2020diffusion\nsed -i 's/approximated efficiently with Sinkhorn-Knopp iterations~\\\\cite{cuturi2013sinkhorn}/approximated efficiently with Sinkhorn-Knopp iterations/' \"$SHARED/method.tex\"\n\nsed -i 's/surpassing domain-specific diffusion models~\\\\cite{hoang2020diffusion}/surpassing domain-specific diffusion models/' \"$SHARED/method.tex\"\n\necho \"Method fixed\"\n\n# Fix experiments.tex - remove scikit-learn\nsed -i 's/These metrics comprehensively capture diagnostic efficacy, balancing nominal performance with degradation resilience \\\\cite{scikit-learn}./These metrics comprehensively capture diagnostic efficacy, balancing nominal 