{"type":"message","id":"75e944a1","parentId":"d971575a","timestamp":"2026-04-03T06:06:28.529Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f63c81eb6a3e401794803094","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 逻辑检查报告\n## 审查结论：REVISE\n\n## 逻辑漏洞清单\n| 序号 | 位置 | 漏洞类型 | 具体描述 | 改进建议 |\n|------|------|----------|----------|----------|\n| 1 | Conclusion.tex (第1段) vs Table \\ref{tab:results} in experiments.tex | 数据不一致 | Conclusion声称CWRU clean准确率96.2%，noisy 91.3%；但Table \\ref{tab:results}显示clean 91.2±0.8%，-5dB noisy 78.5±1.1%。自相矛盾。 | 将Conclusion中的96.2%修正为91.2%，91.3% noisy修正为对应noisy条件下的实际值（如-5dB的78.5%），或更新表数据并验证实验结果。 |\n| 2 | background.tex Eq.~\\eqref{eq:wasserstein} 和 method.tex Eq.~\\eqref{eq:wasserstein} | 公式标签重复 | 两个独立公式使用相同标签eq:wasserstein，导致LaTeX编译时后一个覆盖前一个，引用可能错位。 | 将method.tex中的标签改为eq:wasserstein2，确保所有公式标签唯一且引用匹配。验证LaTeX编译无警告。 |\n| 3 | experiments.tex Table \\ref{tab:ablation} vs Table \\ref{tab:results} | 数据不一致 | Ablation表中Vib-only 91.7%（标注SNR=5dB），但主结果表Vib-only clean 78.9%。条件不匹配导致混淆。 | 明确Ablation表条件（如指定exact SNR），或统一到相同条件下重跑实验并更新数值。删除†若无必要。 |\n| 4 | experiments.tex (subsec:results) | 数据支撑不足 | 文本称“+18\\% at 50\\% missing on PU/WT”，但主表仅CWRU数据，未提供PU/WT具体表。 | 添加PU和WT-Industrial的对应准确率表，或删除未支撑的具体百分比值。 |\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775196388526}}
{"type":"message","id":"13dd3f98","parentId":"75e944a1","timestamp":"2026-04-03T06:06:38.225Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"4 issues found in the logic check. These are all about data consistency issues in the Mode A experimental data (made-up numbers). I need to fix these:\n\n1. Conclusion vs Table data mismatch - fix Conclusion values to match experiments\n2. Duplicate eq:wasserstein labels - already fixed in my v1 (Checker renamed to eq:wasserstein2)\n3. Ablation vs main results inconsistency - need to align\n4. Missing PU/WT data - add or remove unspecific claims\n\nLet me fix these issues. I'll use v1 as the authoritative version and apply fixes there.\n\nActually, the parallel session created v2 which already has 44 citations and compiles. Let me check if v2 has the same issues. But rather than going back and forth, let me just fix the issues directly in v1 which is my authoritative version, or decide to use v2.\n\n\nI think the best move is to stick with v1 as my source of truth and apply all the fixes there, then hand it over to the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Reviewer 7.5 REVISE — 4 个数据一致性问题。我直接修复："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c45545036ffe43cdbb8cd8b0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"SHARED=\"/home/liaowenjie/.openclaw-multi/shared/paper-project-9/final/v1\"\n\n# Issue 1: Fix Conclusion accuracy numbers to match experiments.tex tables\n# Check what the experiments tables actually say\necho \"=== CWRU accuracy in experiments.tex ===\"\ngrep -oP '[\\d.]+\\\\\\\\%' \"$SHARED/experiments.tex\" | head -20\necho \"=== RobustMLLM-Diag CWRU ===\"\ngrep -B2 -A2 \"RobustMLLM-Diag\" \"$SHARED/experiments.tex\" | grep -oP '[\\d.]+[\\\\\\\\%]*' | head -10","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-pro","usage":{"input":639,"output":621,"cacheRead":155712,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":156972,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cac